generalDescription: This test case describes when a patient is administered a first dose of  the Covid-19 vaccine as AstraZeneca and a second dose of the Covid-19 vaccine as Sinovac that both doses are valid.  A booster (bivalent preferred) dose should be forecast in 8 weeks.
